---
title: Smart Double Chicken and Wild Rice Stew with Spinach and Mirepoix
description: Chicken, wild rice, veggies and a white-wine scented broth make for coziness in a bowl. Cook the rice separately to speed up this simple supper!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/ragout-de-poulet-double-et-de-riz-sauvage-c889280f.jpg
